I love @luxuryyoni ❤️. You all need to go follow them now! This black woman owned business by @felifabulous is setting the trend for natural feminine care and building confidence 😊.  @luxuryyoni Royal Throne is a product that I swear by, it’s helped me tremendously with relaxing my mind plus their steam herbs smell amazing ☘️, is always fresh and have so many benefits like helping with cramps and heavy flow, balancing the pH etc. I love setting a relaxing mood at night 🧖🏾‍♀️ with my incense and steam herbs, putting on my Luxury Diva Gown for comfort and just sitting on my throne for 20 to 30 minutes.

If you don’t have a Royal throne you NEED one now. Follow @luxuryyoni then go to their website www.luxuryyoni.com to get yours and use my code Angela15 for $$ off. Tell them I sent you 😉
